														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1883293">
									

<p>It makes sense to me&#8212; being a linguist, Dr. R is able to find syntax and grammar patterns in the otherwise generally unknown language. Using those, one can figure out the rest of the words bit by bit, along with other techniques to learn what's what.</p>
<p>Incredibly difficult and time-consuming, but it <em>does</em> say &quot;after several weeks of work.&quot;</p>
<p>As for the rest of it, I like it! Definitely a nice way to play on the old tales.</p>

