<p>I like the SCiP but I don't think this log tells us anything we don't already know. Can't upvote it.</p>
<p>It's well written, the conversation is natural enough, and the situation seems at least plausible <em>enough</em> that I can suspend my disbelief for it. Can't downvote it.</p>
<p>So this one's a 0. However, SCP-1372 gets the plus. If for no other reason than being &quot;the edge of the world&quot;. I'm surprised you were able to write it up so effectively.</p>

